-- Beijing Enterprises Water Reports 33% Jump in Earnings
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2013-08-29T09:38:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-29/beijing-enterprises-water-reports-33-jump-in-earnings.html
Beijing Enterprises Water Group Ltd. (371) 
reported a 33 percent increase in first-half profit as earnings
from water-treatment and construction services grew.  Net income rose to HK$514.3 million ($66 million) from
HK$386.6 million a year earlier, the company said today in a
filing to the Hong Kong stock exchange. Sales almost doubled to
HK$2.76 billion.  Beijing Enterprises “maintained a steady growth in the
first half,” the company said. Water-treatment and construction
services together generated 96 percent of profit, up from 79
percent a year earlier.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
